### Diagnóstico de Visibilidad en Google Ads (Ad Rank vs. Budget)
* **Señal Técnica:** Framework de depuración operativa para campañas SaaS; aísla variables (presupuesto, pujas, relevancia) en lugar de escalar gasto a ciegas.
* **Contenido Crudo:**
> “Why aren’t we showing up at the top of Google?”
> There are only 2 real answers. Most teams fix the wrong one ⤵️
> 
> If competitors are outranking you, most teams jump straight to:
> → Increase budget
> → Rewrite ads
> → Launch new campaigns
> 
> But that’s backwards. Here’s what we've found work across $4M/month in GA spend👇
> 
> 1/ See where you stand
> If you don’t know your impression share or who’s beating you, you’re guessing. Check Auction Insights. Find the gap.
> 
> 2/ Find the leak
> Low impression share usually comes down to Budget or Ad Rank. Fix the right one.
> 
> 3/ Fix your rank (fastest lever)
> If budget isn’t the issue, your bids are. Increase bid caps and monitor search lost to rank.
> 
> 4/ Fix your quality score (long-term lever)
> If bids don’t move the needle, your relevance is the problem:
> → Ads not matching keywords
> → Weak CTR
> → Poor landing page experience
> 
> Most teams try to fix everything at once. That’s why nothing works. The real play is diagnosing the bottleneck first. Because you can’t fix what you can’t see.

