### Arquitectura de Segmentación Temprana en ChatGPT Ads
* **Señal Técnica:** Análisis de la transición de búsqueda semántica transaccional (keywords) a intención conversacional profunda ("Context Hints") en ecosistemas LLM.
* **Contenido Crudo:**
> We just got access to ChatGPT Ads, and there's one thing that caught my attention: the targeting.
> 
> It's different from what I've seen on other platforms. Instead of keywords, you're providing written context for when your ad should appear. They call it "context hints".
> 
> I'm still figuring out what that means in practice, but it makes perfect sense since your ads will be showing up in the "middle" of a conversation.
> 
> The rest of the hierarchy is very similar to what you see on Google, Meta, or LinkedIn. Since it's early access, there are several limitations as expected:
> 👉 Only 1 available campaign objective 
> 👉 Only a handful of metrics available
> 
> We'll be piloting this with 5 clients and for our own agency over the next few weeks, so I'll share more in the coming weeks.

